headline: Humana Inc. Announces Dates for First Quarter 2025 Earnings and June Investor Conference
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., April 03, 2025--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) will release financial results for the first quarter 2025 (1Q25) and host a live question-and-answer session on Wednesday, April 30, 2025. Additionally, the company will host an Investor Conference on Monday, June 16, 2025.

headline: 3 HMO Stocks to Watch Amid Nurse Shortages, High Tech Costs
summary: The Medical-HMO industry rides on steady premium flows resulting from a growing customer base and contract wins. However, industry headwinds like elevated technology costs and workforce shortages remain concerns. UNH, HUM and CNC are likely to navigate industry storms.
